Package: ginkos-defaults
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Rizalina Mingazheva <rizalina.mingazheva@gmail.com>
Depends: i3, i3status, alacritty, rofi, feh, picom, fonts-noto
Description: GinkOS default configuration and branding
 Provides the default i3 window manager configuration,
 terminal settings, application launcher theme, wallpaper,
 and system branding for GinkOS 1.0 (maidenhair).
